data.description: Nestled in a charming neighborhood near Lamar Elementary, this pristine property blends comfort and convenience and reflects the care and attention given by its owners. The open concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. This home also offers a flexible room, perfect for a home office or personal workout sanctuary. No carpet is in this home; low maintenance flooring enhances the overall cleanliness and modern aesthetic. Outside, you will find a nice above-ground pool for cooling off on our hot summer days. Extra concrete on the driveway and side of the yard provides ample parking space. A solar ventilation system in the attic provides energy savings. This peaceful retreat may just be your next place you call home; call your agent today to set up a time to visit.
